name: Dark Matter - FTC Team 4150
body:
#We are _**Dark Matter**_
###We believe in sharing what we learn with the rest of the world, weather it be the code we write, the curriculum we develop, or anything else. 

**Our Mission**
>The FIRST program has made a difference in our lives and it is important for us to promote and provide the same opportunities to kids of all ages, by partnering with like-minded organizations

**Our Vision:**
>To inspire people to work with us in order to solve today's problems

***
Learn more about our team: [About Us](https://github.com/DarkMatter4150/Code/wiki/About-Us)

Follow what we are learning: [Code Wiki](https://github.com/DarkMatter4150/Code/wiki)

Contact us: `DarkMatter4150@gmail.com`

Follow us on Twitter: [@DarkMatter4150](twitter.com/darkmatter4150)
